{"uuid":"recommended239070","createDate":1615674720000,"customConfigJson":"{\"gameId\":\"239070\",\"readError\":\"false\",\"syncTime\":\"2024-04-30 12:10:36\",\"ratingSummary\":\"推荐\",\"postTime\":\"2021-03-14\",\"gameName\":\"Hammerwatch\",\"gameLink\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/239070\",\"recommendedLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/id/oneness629/recommended/239070/\",\"playTime\":\"8.6\",\"updateTime\":\"2021-03-14\",\"reviewPlayTime\":\"8.6\",\"communityLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/239070\"}","title":"评测 > Hammerwatch","content":"<div id=\"ReviewText\">\n &lt;铁锤守卫&gt; 2D类魂类迷宫冒险游戏，有汉化，汉化效果很棒！\n <br>\n 剧情模式下有7种职业2张大型迷宫可供玩家探索！\n <br>\n 自定义模式支持老版本的迷宫、生存模式、防御模式3种！\n <br>\n 支持多人合作！再配合美丽的背景音乐岂不美滋滋？？\n <br>\n 还支持工坊任务编辑器！\n <br>\n <br>\n 游戏没有升级制度，只有地图上捡起各种物资和金钱，通过金钱去购买升级选项！\n <br>\n 路上一堆堆的箱子和怪物，基本一路捡垃圾，而且可以捡得干干净净！！\n <br>\n <div class=\"bb_h1\">\n  像环卫工人一样一路上把能破坏的能捡的垃圾清理的干干净净\n </div>\n <br>\n 但实际是迷宫很大，很烦，地图默认全屏显示，虽然可以设置半透明，但是实际玩起来要么地图遮挡视线没注意到机关！要么看到机关但是地图却不支持移动导致不清楚到底哪些区域是没解锁的迷雾状态！！总是不尽人意！！\n <br>\n 而且每个地图都要分别打开特定的机关后才能去打Boss！！迷宫+机关更加恶心！！\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2424603040\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_0\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2424603040</a>\n <br>\n 铁锤城堡还好，毕竟迷宫墙壁很明显，太阳神殿那种像透明墙的墙壁真的是···\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2424604179\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_1\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2424604179</a>\n <br>\n <div class=\"bb_h1\">\n  游戏对路痴不太友好\n </div>~反正我是迷路了~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2424605738\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_2\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2424605738</a>\n</div>\n<div id=\"ReviewEdit\" style=\"display: none\">\n <textarea id=\"ReviewEditTextArea\" class=\"review_edit_text_area\" maxlength=\"8000\" rows=\"2\" c